            complex repairs, like compressor replacement, can be pricier, potentially
            ranging from <b>$500 to $800</b>. Whirlpool's extensive network
            of authorized repair technicians can sometimes help reduce costs
            by ensuring that replacements and repairs use genuine parts,
            thereby extending the lifespan of the appliance.
