          <h3>Samsung</h3>
          <p>
            Samsung refrigerators are renowned for their advanced technology
            and sleek designs, often featuring digital displays, smart
            capabilities, and multiple cooling zones. The cost to repair a
            Samsung refrigerator can be on the higher side due to these
            sophisticated features. Typical repair costs can range from <b
