            compared to more technologically advanced brands. Typical repair
            expenses might range from <b>$150 to $300</b> for issues like a faulty
            defrost timer or a broken door gasket. If more extensive repairs
            are needed, such as replacing the compressor, costs can climb to
            between <b>$500 and $750</b>. Maytag's reputation for
